What to Do After Setup

Once all four steps are done, here is how to start building:

Navigate to your project folder in the terminal
cd /path/to/your/project

Start Claude Code
claude

Describe the website you want to build
> Build me an animated landing page for a SaaS product.
> Use Framer Motion for scroll animations.
> Include a hero, features section, pricing, and footer.

🎯 Pro Tip: The more specific you are in your prompt, the better the output. Describe the vibe, the sections you need, and any specific animations or interactions you have in mind.




